CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 12, 1941, pg. 8, reads: "Pretty Jackson-Cralle Nuptials Bring Socialites Together In Festive Affair - The Jackson-Cralle nuptials last Saturday evening proved one of smoke town's smartest affairs... the groomsmen Allen Goode, best man, Kenneth Wiggins, Frank Bolden, Joseph Cralle, and William Ware... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men in wedding party, from left: Allen Goode, Kenneth Wiggins, Frank Bolden, Joseph Cralle, and William Ware, standing in Loendi Club for Jackson - Cralle wedding
